(28, 18, 13, 49, 85, '65\" 4K Curved Smart LED TV with HDR and Dolby Audio', '1387140', 1, '141', '6742ed5a95399.png', 'Immerse yourself in a stunning 65\" 4K curved display with HDR and Dolby Audio. This Smart LED TV offers an exceptional cinematic experience from every angle.', '<p>Step into a new dimension of entertainment with the 65\" 4K Curved Smart LED TV. Its elegant curved design creates an immersive viewing experience, wrapping you in rich visuals and lifelike detail. With 4K Ultra HD resolution and HDR technology, every scene bursts with vibrant colors, deep blacks, and sharp contrast. Dolby Audio delivers powerful, theater-like sound, enhancing your favorite movies and games. The built-in smart platform offers seamless access to popular streaming services and voice control for hands-free operation. Sleek and sophisticated, this TV is a perfect addition to any modern living space.</p>', '799.99', '1099.99', '{\"Color\":{\"option_id\":244,\"name\":\"Black\",\"price\":50,\"stock\":100},\"Audio Technology\":{\"option_id\":247,\"name\":\"Dolby Atmos\",\"price\":35,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-25 06:44:04', NULL),
(29, 19, 13, 49, 89, 'Portable Bluetooth Speaker with 360° Sound and 12-Hour Battery', '2594618', 1, '135', '6742f0f0428d7.png', 'A compact and powerful portable Bluetooth speaker offering 360° sound, water resistance, and up to 12 hours of playtime—perfect for outdoor adventures and parties.', '<p>Enjoy premium sound wherever you go with the Portable Bluetooth Speaker. Designed for on-the-go listening, this speaker delivers rich, clear, and powerful 360° sound, filling your surroundings with music from every angle. With a durable, water-resistant design, it’s ideal for outdoor use, whether you\'re at the beach, hiking, or hosting a backyard party. The long-lasting 12-hour battery ensures uninterrupted playtime throughout the day. Bluetooth connectivity allows seamless pairing with your devices, while the compact size makes it easy to carry. Elevate your music experience with this portable and versatile speaker, built for both style and performance.</p>', '79.99', '99.99', '{\"Size\":{\"option_id\":235,\"name\":\"Large\",\"price\":5,\"stock\":100},\"Color\":{\"option_id\":239,\"name\":\"Silver\",\"price\":12,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-25 06:45:18', NULL),
(30, 19, 13, 49, 81, 'Ultra-Slim 10.1\" Android Tablet with 64GB Storage', '7921025', 1, '131', '6742ebfc5b8ca.png', 'A lightweight, high-performance 10.1\" Android tablet featuring 64GB storage, a vibrant HD display, and long battery life. Perfect for entertainment, work, and learning on the go.', '<p>Enhance your digital experience with the Ultra-Slim 10.1\" Android Tablet. This sleek tablet offers a stunning HD display, delivering sharp visuals and vibrant colors, ideal for streaming, reading, or gaming. With 64GB of internal storage (expandable via microSD), you have ample space for apps, photos, and videos. The powerful processor ensures smooth multitasking, while the long-lasting battery keeps you connected throughout the day. Lightweight and portable, it\'s perfect for students, professionals, or casual users. Enjoy seamless connectivity with Wi-Fi and Bluetooth, and capture memories with the front and rear cameras.</p>', '175.99', '249.99', '{\"Storage\":{\"option_id\":253,\"name\":\"128GB\",\"price\":100,\"stock\":100},\"Color\":{\"option_id\":255,\"name\":\"Silver\",\"price\":100,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-25 06:45:18', NULL),
(31, 19, 13, 49, 77, 'High-Speed Dual-Band Wi-Fi 6 Router with 3000Mbps', '6175717', 1, '145', '6742ea862162e.png', 'A powerful dual-band Wi-Fi 6 router delivering up to 3000Mbps for seamless streaming, gaming, and browsing. Ideal for homes and small offices requiring fast, stable connections.', '<p>Experience lightning-fast connectivity with our High-Speed Dual-Band Wi-Fi 6 Router. Engineered for modern homes and offices, this router offers a combined speed of up to 3000Mbps across dual bands (2.4GHz and 5GHz). Wi-Fi 6 technology ensures faster data transfers, improved capacity, and reduced latency, making it perfect for HD streaming, online gaming, and video conferencing. With MU-MIMO support, multiple devices can connect without compromising speed or stability. The router\'s sleek design fits any space, while advanced security protocols protect your network from threats. Stay connected and in control with an easy-to-use mobile app for network management.</p>', '129.99', '179.99', '{\"Color\":{\"option_id\":266,\"name\":\"White\",\"price\":5,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-25 06:45:18', NULL),
(32, 19, 13, 49, 80, 'Advanced 5G Smartphone with 128GB Storage and Triple Camera', '3148914', 1, '131', '6742eba399114.png', 'A sleek and powerful 5G smartphone featuring a stunning display, triple-lens camera system, and 128GB of storage. Ideal for photography, gaming, and multitasking.', '<p>Experience next-level performance with the Advanced 5G Smartphone. Powered by a high-speed processor and equipped with 128GB of storage, this smartphone ensures seamless multitasking, gaming, and media streaming. The 6.5\" AMOLED display offers vibrant visuals with stunning clarity, perfect for watching videos or browsing. Capture breathtaking photos and videos with the triple-lens camera system, including wide, ultra-wide, and macro lenses. Stay connected with lightning-fast 5G connectivity and enjoy all-day battery life with fast charging support. With a sleek, modern design and advanced security features, this smartphone is the ultimate tool for work and play.</p>', '499.99', '649.99', '{\"Storage\":{\"option_id\":256,\"name\":\"64GB\",\"price\":100,\"stock\":100},\"Color\":{\"option_id\":261,\"name\":\"Black\",\"price\":10,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-25 06:45:18', NULL),
(33, 20, 13, 49, 84, '55\" 4K Smart LED TV with HDR and Voice Control', '9774557', 1, '141', '6742ed03e86bf.png', 'A sleek 55\" 4K Smart LED TV featuring HDR technology and voice control. Enjoy stunning visuals, smart apps, and seamless streaming for an ultimate viewing experience.', '<p>Experience true-to-life picture quality with the 55\" 4K Smart LED TV. Equipped with HDR technology, this TV delivers stunning contrast, vivid colors, and sharp detail, bringing your favorite movies and shows to life. The built-in smart platform gives you access to popular streaming apps like Netflix, YouTube, and Prime Video. Integrated voice control lets you navigate effortlessly, while multiple HDMI and USB ports ensure easy connectivity with other devices. Its slim, modern design enhances any living space, providing both elegance and entertainment. Perfect for families, gamers, and movie enthusiasts.</p>', '399.99', '599.99', '{\"Color\":{\"option_id\":248,\"name\":\"Black\",\"price\":50,\"stock\":100},\"Audio Technology\":{\"option_id\":251,\"name\":\"Dolby Atmos\",\"price\":52,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-25 06:48:08', NULL),
(34, 21, 14, 50, 117, 'Insulated Kids\' Lunch Box – Spacious, Fun, and Perfect for Keeping Meals Fresh', '5304757', 1, '155', '67445e800bbce.png', 'Our Insulated Kids\' Lunch Box keeps meals fresh and cool throughout the day. With a spacious design, easy-to-carry handle, and fun, colorful patterns, it\'s perfect for school lunches, picnics, and after-school snacks.', '<p>Make lunchtime fun and fresh with our <em>Insulated Kids\' Lunch Box</em>! Designed with busy kids in mind, this lunch box features an insulated lining to keep meals cool and fresh until it’s time to eat. Whether it\'s a sandwich, fruit, or snacks, this lunch box ensures everything stays at the perfect temperature for longer.</p>\r\n<p>Crafted from durable, BPA-free materials, the lunch box is built to withstand daily use while remaining lightweight and easy to carry. The sturdy handle makes it simple for kids to carry their lunch box wherever they go, and the spacious interior offers plenty of room for all their favorite meals.</p>\r\n<p>The fun, vibrant designs—featuring characters, patterns, and colors kids love—add an element of excitement to lunchtime. It also includes an easy-to-clean lining, making it simple to wipe down and maintain.</p>\r\n<p>Perfect for school, sports, or family outings, the <em>Insulated Kids\' Lunch Box</em> is both practical and playful, making it a must-have for every child\'s lunchtime routine.</p>', '18.99', '29.99', NULL, '2024-11-26 06:26:27', NULL),
(35, 21, 14, 50, 116, 'Eco-Friendly Kids\' Water Bottle – Durable, Leak-Proof, and Perfect for Hydration on the Go', '5652534', 1, '155', '67445e212d1cc.png', 'Our Eco-Friendly Kids\' Water Bottle is designed to keep your child hydrated throughout the day. Featuring a durable, leak-proof design and fun, colorful patterns, it’s the perfect companion for school, sports, and outdoor adventures.', '<p>Keep your little one refreshed and hydrated with our <em>Eco-Friendly Kids\' Water Bottle</em>! This bottle is made from high-quality, BPA-free materials that are safe for kids and the environment. Its durable construction ensures it can withstand everyday use, whether it’s tossed into a backpack, dropped during play, or used during a sports game.</p>\r\n<p>The bottle features a leak-proof cap, making it easy to carry without worrying about spills. The wide mouth opening allows for easy filling and cleaning, while the ergonomic handle makes it simple for kids to carry. Available in a variety of vibrant colors and fun designs, including characters and patterns that kids love, this water bottle adds a playful touch to their hydration routine.</p>\r\n<p>Lightweight and compact, the <em>Eco-Friendly Kids\' Water Bottle</em> fits perfectly in backpacks, lunch boxes, or sports bags. It’s the ideal choice for staying hydrated at school, on field trips, or during outdoor play.</p>\r\n<p>Made with eco-conscious materials, this bottle is reusable and environmentally friendly, making it a great choice for both your child and the planet.</p>', '14.99', '29.99', '{\"Color\":{\"option_id\":296,\"name\":\"Midnight Blue\",\"price\":1,\"stock\":100},\"Capacity\":{\"option_id\":299,\"name\":\"500ml\",\"price\":5,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-26 06:26:27', NULL),
