(37, 21, 14, 50, 111, 'Ergonomic Kids’ Chairs & Stools – Comfortable, Stylish, and Perfect for Learning and Play', '4384079', 1, '159', '67445600b0377.png', 'Our Ergonomic Kids’ Chairs & Stools provide the perfect combination of comfort, durability, and style. Designed for study rooms, play areas, or dining tables, these chairs and stools support proper posture while adding a fun touch to any space.', '<p>Make learning and playtime more comfortable with our <em>Ergonomic Kids’ Chairs &amp; Stools</em>! Designed with growing children in mind, these chairs and stools offer excellent support and durability for everyday use. Whether they’re used for studying, playing, or relaxing, these pieces are essential for any kid-friendly space.</p>\r\n<p>Crafted from high-quality, sturdy materials, the chairs feature ergonomic designs that promote proper posture, reducing strain during long study sessions or creative activities. The smooth, rounded edges ensure safety, while the non-slip feet provide stability on various surfaces.</p>\r\n<p>Our stools are lightweight and easy to move, perfect for versatile seating solutions in playrooms or classrooms. The stackable design makes storage simple and efficient, saving space when not in use.</p>\r\n<p>Available in vibrant colors and playful designs, these chairs and stools add a fun, cheerful touch to any room. The easy-to-clean surfaces ensure they stay looking new, even with daily use.</p>\r\n<p>Create a comfortable and inspiring environment with our <em>Ergonomic Kids’ Chairs &amp; Stools</em>—ideal for learning, playing, and growing!</p>', '112.99', '295.99', NULL, '2024-11-26 06:26:27', NULL),
(38, 22, 14, 50, 109, 'Ergonomic Study Desk – Adjustable, Durable, and Perfect for Learning and Creativity', '6766922', 1, '159', '6744556bb6f28.png', 'Our Ergonomic Study Desk is designed to enhance focus and comfort. With adjustable height, ample workspace, and durable construction, it’s the perfect addition to any child’s study room, promoting better posture and organized learning.', '<p>Transform your child’s learning environment with our <em>Ergonomic Study Desk</em>! Designed with both functionality and comfort in mind, this desk provides a sturdy and spacious workspace ideal for homework, art projects, and online classes.</p>\r\n<p>The adjustable height feature ensures the desk grows with your child, promoting proper posture and reducing strain during long study sessions. The smooth, scratch-resistant surface is easy to clean and large enough to accommodate books, stationery, and a laptop or tablet.</p>\r\n<p>Constructed from high-quality materials, this desk offers long-lasting durability, with reinforced legs for stability. The built-in storage compartments and shelves help keep essential supplies organized and within reach, reducing clutter and enhancing productivity.</p>', '129.99', '295.99', '{\"Size\":{\"option_id\":320,\"name\":\"3-Tier\",\"price\":40,\"stock\":100},\"Color\":{\"option_id\":323,\"name\":\"Natural Oak\",\"price\":10,\"stock\":10}}', '2024-11-26 06:28:36', NULL),
(39, 22, 14, 50, 107, 'Premium School Shoes – Comfortable, Durable, and Perfect for Everyday School Wear', '8947646', 1, '157', '674454650c803.png', 'Our Premium School Shoes combine durability, comfort, and style. Designed for active kids, these shoes offer all-day support, a sturdy build, and a polished look, making them perfect for school uniforms and daily wear.', '<p>Ensure your child steps into school with confidence and comfort with our <em>Premium School Shoes</em>! Crafted from high-quality materials, these shoes are designed to withstand the rigors of daily school life, providing long-lasting durability without compromising on style.</p>\r\n<p>The soft, cushioned insole and padded collar offer superior comfort, keeping little feet supported throughout the day. Breathable lining ensures proper ventilation, preventing moisture build-up and keeping feet fresh, even during long hours of wear.</p>\r\n<p>The sturdy, non-slip rubber sole provides excellent traction on various surfaces, ensuring safety during playtime and school activities. Reinforced stitching and a durable exterior make these shoes resistant to scuffs and everyday wear and tear, making them ideal for active children.</p>\r\n<p>Featuring a classic, polished design, these shoes are perfect for school uniforms, formal events, or casual wear. Easy-to-fasten options, such as Velcro straps or traditional laces, provide a secure fit and make them easy to put on and take off.</p>', '59.99', '89.99', NULL, '2024-11-26 06:28:36', NULL),
(40, 23, 14, 50, 118, 'Durable Kids\' Pencil Box – Stylish, Spacious, and Perfect for Organizing School Supplies', '8038712', 1, '155', '67445ecf3f8ed.png', 'Our Durable Kids\' Pencil Box is the perfect solution for keeping school supplies organized and easily accessible. With a spacious design, secure closure, and fun, colorful patterns, it’s ideal for pencils, erasers, and other school essentials.', '<p>Keep your child’s school supplies neatly organized with our <em>Durable Kids\' Pencil Box</em>! Designed to hold everything from pencils and pens to erasers and sharpeners, this pencil box is perfect for storing all their essentials in one place.</p>\r\n<p>Made from high-quality, sturdy materials, this pencil box features a secure snap closure to keep contents safe and prevent spills. Its compact size makes it easy to fit into school bags, desks, or lockers, while the vibrant colors and fun designs add a touch of personality to school accessories.</p>\r\n<p>The spacious interior provides plenty of room for all their writing instruments, while the simple, functional design ensures it’s easy for kids to use and keep tidy. Available in a variety of fun designs, including favorite characters and playful patterns, this pencil box will become your child’s go-to organizer.</p>\r\n<p>Whether for school, art projects, or everyday use, the <em>Durable Kids\' Pencil Box</em> is a must-have for young learners. Durable, practical, and fun, it’s the perfect addition to their school supplies collection!</p>', '9.99', '12.99', '{\"Color\":{\"option_id\":292,\"name\":\"Midnight Blue\",\"price\":2,\"stock\":100},\"Size\":{\"option_id\":295,\"name\":\"Jumbo\",\"price\":5,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-26 06:30:24', NULL),
(41, 23, 14, 50, 115, 'Kids\' Active Sportswear Set – Comfortable, Stylish, and Perfect for Every Adventure', '9792679', 1, '147', '67445da5c574c.png', 'Our Kids\' Active Sportswear Set is designed for active kids who love to play, run, and explore. Featuring breathable, stretchable fabrics and a stylish design, this set is perfect for sports, outdoor activities, and casual wear.', '<p>Get your little one ready for their next adventure with our <em>Kids\' Active Sportswear Set</em>! Whether it’s a day at the park, a soccer game, or simply running around with friends, this set offers the perfect combination of style, comfort, and performance.</p>\r\n<p>Crafted from breathable and moisture-wicking fabrics, this sportswear set ensures that your child stays cool and comfortable during even the most intense activities. The stretchable material provides flexibility and freedom of movement, making it ideal for sports like basketball, football, or running.</p>\r\n<p>The set includes a sporty T-shirt and matching shorts, both designed with vibrant colors and fun patterns that kids love. The elastic waistband ensures a snug fit, while the lightweight fabric offers durability and easy maintenance, even after countless washes.</p>\r\n<p>Available in a range of sizes and colors, the <em>Kids\' Active Sportswear Set</em> is perfect for every child who loves to stay active and stylish. Get ready for fun, play, and adventure, all while looking great in this comfortable and versatile sportswear set!</p>', '17.09', '55.99', '{\"Size\":{\"option_id\":300,\"name\":\"6Y\",\"price\":5,\"stock\":100},\"Color\":{\"option_id\":303,\"name\":\"Pink\",\"price\":2,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-26 06:30:24', NULL),
(42, 24, 14, 50, 101, 'Art & Craft Kits – Creative Fun for All Ages', '6563963', 1, '149', '674442abb6d41.png', 'Unleash your creativity with our Art & Craft Kits! Perfect for kids, beginners, or seasoned artists, these kits provide everything you need to craft beautiful, personalized projects and explore your artistic talents.', '<p>Dive into the world of creativity with our <em>Art &amp; Craft Kits</em>! Whether you\'re a budding artist or just looking for a fun, hands-on activity, these all-in-one kits are designed to inspire and engage. Packed with high-quality materials, each kit comes with everything you need to create stunning works of art—from paints and brushes to paper, beads, and more.</p>\r\n<p>Our kits are perfect for kids, teens, and adults alike, offering a variety of craft activities such as painting, drawing, jewelry-making, scrapbooking, and more. Each kit is carefully curated to ensure ease of use, with step-by-step instructions to guide you through each project.</p>\r\n<p>Not only are these Art &amp; Craft Kits an ideal way to spend quality time with family and friends, but they also promote essential skills like fine motor development, creativity, and problem-solving. These kits make excellent gifts for birthdays, holidays, or any occasion that calls for a creative touch.</p>\r\n<p>With a wide range of themes and projects, including seasonal crafts, DIY decorations, and personalized gift ideas, there’s a kit to suit every taste and occasion. Let your imagination run wild and create beautiful, one-of-a-kind pieces with our Art &amp; Craft Kits!</p>', '19.99', '24.99', NULL, '2024-11-26 06:32:04', NULL),
(43, 24, 14, 50, 96, 'Remote-Controlled Toy Truck – Adventure on Wheels', '7954277', 1, '149', '6744407665724.png', 'Fuel your child’s imagination with the Remote-Controlled Toy Truck! This exciting and durable truck brings hours of fun, allowing young drivers to experience the thrill of remote control action while navigating through their own mini adventures.', '<p>Get ready for an action-packed ride with the <em>Remote-Controlled Toy Truck</em>! Built for both indoor and outdoor play, this sturdy truck features an easy-to-use remote that lets your child steer, accelerate, and even perform stunts with just the push of a button. Whether it\'s racing across the living room or conquering the backyard, this truck offers the perfect balance of fun and adventure.</p>\r\n<p>The toy truck is designed for children aged 3 and up and comes with a robust build to handle bumps and falls. With large wheels, it effortlessly glides over various terrains, allowing your child to explore different environments and create exciting races or obstacle courses.</p>\r\n<p>The intuitive remote controller is simple enough for younger children to use, providing both forward and backward movement, as well as a 360-degree turning radius. Its sleek design and vibrant colors make it a standout toy that will keep your child entertained for hours.</p>\r\n<p>Perfect as a birthday gift or a special treat, the Remote-Controlled Toy Truck is sure to be a hit with any young vehicle enthusiast!</p>', '39.99', '49.99', '{\"Size\":{\"option_id\":348,\"name\":\"1:16 Scale\",\"price\":10,\"stock\":100},\"Color\":{\"option_id\":351,\"name\":\"Yellow\",\"price\":5,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-26 06:32:04', NULL),
