(109, 70, 10, 56, 12, 'Delicious Chicken Sharma – Tender, Flavorful & Spiced to Perfection', '3205808', 1, '81', '6734747c4ab7d.png', 'Our Chicken Sharma is a mouthwatering blend of tender chicken marinated in aromatic spices, grilled to perfection, and served with your choice of fresh vegetables, sauces, and warm pita bread. It\'s the perfect option for a satisfying, flavorful meal.', '<p>Indulge in the irresistible taste of our <strong>Chicken Sharma</strong>, a dish that combines succulent, tender chicken with a unique blend of spices and flavors. The chicken is marinated in a rich mixture of aromatic spices, then grilled to perfection, ensuring every bite is packed with savory goodness.</p>\r\n<p>Served with fresh, crunchy vegetables, and your choice of sauces wrapped in warm, soft pita bread, <strong>Chicken Sharma</strong> is a flavorful feast that brings together the best of Middle Eastern cuisine. Each bite delivers the perfect balance of tender chicken, zesty spices, and creamy sauces, all tucked into a warm and fluffy pita.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you’re enjoying a quick lunch, dinner, or snack, <strong>Chicken Sharma</strong> is a satisfying choice that offers rich flavors and textures with every bite. It\'s an excellent option for anyone who loves bold, flavorful meals.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Chicken Sharma?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Succulent &amp; Flavorful Chicken:</strong> Marinated and grilled to perfection for a tender, juicy bite.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Aromatic Spices:</strong> A unique blend of spices that gives the chicken its distinctive flavor.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fresh Vegetables:</strong> Crisp, fresh vegetables add the perfect crunch and balance.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Choice of Sauces:</strong> Customize your Chicken Sharma with a variety of sauces to suit your taste.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Perfectly Wrapped in Pita:</strong> Soft, warm pita bread keeps everything together, making it easy to enjoy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Key Fea